<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>Nullpointerexception on ErrorCode — Error Code Reference &amp; Solutions</title><link>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/tags/nullpointerexception/</link><description>Recent content in Nullpointerexception on ErrorCode — Error Code Reference &amp; Solutions</description><generator>Hugo</generator><language>en</language><atom:link href="https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/tags/nullpointerexception/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>[Solution] Java NullPointerException on Collection Operations Fix</title><link>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/java/nullpointer-collection/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/java/nullpointer-collection/</guid><description>&lt;h1 id="nullpointerexception-on-collection-operations"&gt;NullPointerException on Collection Operations&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;A &lt;code&gt;NullPointerException&lt;/code&gt; during collection operations is one of the most common Java runtime errors. It occurs when you call methods like &lt;code&gt;.size()&lt;/code&gt;, &lt;code&gt;.get()&lt;/code&gt;, &lt;code&gt;.contains()&lt;/code&gt;, &lt;code&gt;.add()&lt;/code&gt;, or &lt;code&gt;.stream()&lt;/code&gt; on a collection reference that is &lt;code&gt;null&lt;/code&gt;, or when collection elements are &lt;code&gt;null&lt;/code&gt; and you dereference them.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id="description"&gt;Description&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Collections in Java are reference types. A &lt;code&gt;List&lt;/code&gt;, &lt;code&gt;Map&lt;/code&gt;, or &lt;code&gt;Set&lt;/code&gt; variable can be &lt;code&gt;null&lt;/code&gt;, and calling any method on it will throw NPE. Additionally, the collection itself may be non-null but contain &lt;code&gt;null&lt;/code&gt; elements that cause NPE when accessed and dereferenced.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>[Solution] Kotlin NullPointerException — Null Reference Fix</title><link>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/kotlin/null-pointer/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/kotlin/null-pointer/</guid><description>&lt;h1 id="nullpointerexception--null-reference-fix"&gt;NullPointerException — Null Reference Fix&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;A &lt;code&gt;NullPointerException&lt;/code&gt; is thrown when you attempt to dereference an object reference that is &lt;code&gt;null&lt;/code&gt;. Kotlin&amp;rsquo;s type system is designed to eliminate these, but they can still occur in certain situations.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id="description"&gt;Description&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Kotlin distinguishes between nullable and non-nullable types at compile time. However, NPEs can still happen when using platform types from Java, the &lt;code&gt;!!&lt;/code&gt; operator, uninitialized &lt;code&gt;lateinit&lt;/code&gt; variables, or untrusted data.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Common scenarios:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Using the &lt;code&gt;!!&lt;/code&gt; operator on a null value&lt;/strong&gt; — force-unwrapping a nullable reference.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Java interop&lt;/strong&gt; — receiving a null from Java code into a non-nullable Kotlin type.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Accessing an uninitialized &lt;code&gt;lateinit&lt;/code&gt; variable&lt;/strong&gt; — calling methods before assignment.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;External JSON or config data&lt;/strong&gt; — values that may be absent at runtime.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2 id="common-causes"&gt;Common Causes&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-kotlin" data-lang="kotlin"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Cause 1: Force-unwrap with !!
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;val&lt;/span&gt; name: String? = &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;null&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;println(name&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;!!&lt;/span&gt;.length) &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// NullPointerException
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Cause 2: Java interop returning null into non-nullable type
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;val&lt;/span&gt; javaList: JavaList&amp;lt;String&amp;gt; = getJavaList() &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Java method may return null
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;val&lt;/span&gt; first: String = javaList.&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;get&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;0&lt;/span&gt;) &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// NullPointerException if list is null
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Cause 3: Uninitialized lateinit property
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;class&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;User&lt;/span&gt; {
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;lateinit&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;var&lt;/span&gt; name: String
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;fun&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;greet&lt;/span&gt;() = println(&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;Hello, &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;$name&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;)
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;}
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;val&lt;/span&gt; user = User()
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;user.greet() &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// UninitializedPropertyAccessException (subclass of NPE)
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Cause 4: Unsafe cast of null
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;val&lt;/span&gt; data: Any? = &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;null&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;val&lt;/span&gt; str: String = &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;data&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;as&lt;/span&gt; String &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// ClassCastException, but can also trigger NPE
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 id="solutions"&gt;Solutions&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;h3 id="fix-1-use-safe-call-operator-"&gt;Fix 1: Use safe call operator &lt;code&gt;?.&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-kotlin" data-lang="kotlin"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Wrong
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;val&lt;/span&gt; name: String? = &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;null&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;println(name&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;!!&lt;/span&gt;.length) &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// NullPointerException
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Correct
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;println(name&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;?.&lt;/span&gt;length) &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Prints null, no exception
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h3 id="fix-2-use-the-elvis-operator--for-defaults"&gt;Fix 2: Use the Elvis operator &lt;code&gt;?:&lt;/code&gt; for defaults&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-kotlin" data-lang="kotlin"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Wrong
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;val&lt;/span&gt; name: String? = &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;null&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;val&lt;/span&gt; length = name&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;!!&lt;/span&gt;.length &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// NullPointerException
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Correct
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;val&lt;/span&gt; length = name&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;?.&lt;/span&gt;length &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;?:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;0&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Returns 0 if name is null
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h3 id="fix-3-use-let-blocks-for-scoped-null-checks"&gt;Fix 3: Use &lt;code&gt;let&lt;/code&gt; blocks for scoped null checks&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-kotlin" data-lang="kotlin"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Wrong
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;val&lt;/span&gt; name: String? = getName()
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;println(name&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;!!&lt;/span&gt;.uppercase()) &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// NullPointerException if null
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Correct
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;name&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;?.&lt;/span&gt;let {
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; println(&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;it&lt;/span&gt;.uppercase()) &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Only executes if name is not null
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;} &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;?:&lt;/span&gt; println(&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;Name is null&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;)
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h3 id="fix-4-check-lateinit-before-use"&gt;Fix 4: Check &lt;code&gt;lateinit&lt;/code&gt; before use&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-kotlin" data-lang="kotlin"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Wrong
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;class&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;User&lt;/span&gt; {
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;lateinit&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;var&lt;/span&gt; name: String
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;fun&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;greet&lt;/span&gt;() = println(&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;Hello, &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;$name&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;)
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;}
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Correct
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;class&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;User&lt;/span&gt; {
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;lateinit&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;var&lt;/span&gt; name: String
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;fun&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;greet&lt;/span&gt;() {
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;if&lt;/span&gt; (&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;::&lt;/span&gt;name.isInitialized) {
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; println(&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;Hello, &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;$name&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;)
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; } &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;else&lt;/span&gt; {
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; println(&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;Name not set&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;)
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; }
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; }
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;}
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h3 id="fix-5-handle-java-nulls-explicitly"&gt;Fix 5: Handle Java nulls explicitly&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-kotlin" data-lang="kotlin"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Wrong — trusting Java to never return null
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;val&lt;/span&gt; result: String = javaMethod() &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// May throw NPE
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Correct
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;val&lt;/span&gt; result: String? = javaMethod()
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;val&lt;/span&gt; safeResult = result &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;?:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;default&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 id="examples"&gt;Examples&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-kotlin" data-lang="kotlin"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;fun&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;main&lt;/span&gt;() {
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;val&lt;/span&gt; nullable: String? = &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;null&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// This will throw NullPointerException
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// println(nullable!!.length)
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Safe alternatives
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; println(nullable&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;?.&lt;/span&gt;length) &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// null
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; println(nullable&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;?.&lt;/span&gt;length &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;?:&lt;/span&gt; -&lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;1&lt;/span&gt;) &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// -1
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; nullable&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;?.&lt;/span&gt;let {
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; println(&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;it&lt;/span&gt;.length)
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; } &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;?:&lt;/span&gt; println(&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;Value was null&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;)
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;}
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 id="related-errors"&gt;Related Errors&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/kotlin/class-cast/"&gt;ClassCastException&lt;/a&gt; — wrong type cast at runtime.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/kotlin/null-pointer/"&gt;UninitializedPropertyAccessException&lt;/a&gt; — accessing &lt;code&gt;lateinit&lt;/code&gt; before initialization.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/kotlin/illegal-argument/"&gt;IllegalArgumentException&lt;/a&gt; — invalid argument passed to a method.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;</description></item><item><title>[Solution] Kotlin NullPointerException — Null Safety Fix</title><link>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/kotlin/nullpointer-kotlin/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/kotlin/nullpointer-kotlin/</guid><description>&lt;h1 id="nullpointerexception--null-safety-fix"&gt;NullPointerException — Null Safety Fix&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;A &lt;code&gt;NullPointerException&lt;/code&gt; occurs when you attempt to dereference a null reference, bypassing Kotlin&amp;rsquo;s null safety system.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id="description"&gt;Description&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Kotlin&amp;rsquo;s type system distinguishes between nullable and non-nullable types at compile time. However, NPEs can still occur when using the &lt;code&gt;!!&lt;/code&gt; operator, Java interop, or uninitialized &lt;code&gt;lateinit&lt;/code&gt; variables.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Common causes:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Force unwrap with &lt;code&gt;!!&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/strong&gt; — explicitly allowing null dereference&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Java interop&lt;/strong&gt; — receiving null from Java into non-nullable type&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Uninitialized &lt;code&gt;lateinit&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/strong&gt; — accessing before assignment&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Platform types&lt;/strong&gt; — null from external sources&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2 id="common-causes"&gt;Common Causes&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-kotlin" data-lang="kotlin"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Cause 1: Force unwrap with !!
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;val&lt;/span&gt; name: String? = &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;null&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;println(name&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;!!&lt;/span&gt;.length) &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// NullPointerException
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Cause 2: Java interop returning null
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;val&lt;/span&gt; javaList: JavaList&amp;lt;String&amp;gt; = getJavaList()
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;val&lt;/span&gt; first: String = javaList.&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;get&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;0&lt;/span&gt;) &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// NPE if list is null
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Cause 3: Uninitialized lateinit
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;class&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;User&lt;/span&gt; {
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;lateinit&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;var&lt;/span&gt; name: String
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;fun&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;greet&lt;/span&gt;() = println(&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;Hello, &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;$name&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;)
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;}
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;val&lt;/span&gt; user = User()
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;user.greet() &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// UninitializedPropertyAccessException
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Cause 4: Unsafe cast
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;val&lt;/span&gt; data: Any? = &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;null&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;val&lt;/span&gt; str: String = &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;data&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;as&lt;/span&gt; String &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// ClassCastException/NPE
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 id="how-to-fix"&gt;How to Fix&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;h3 id="fix-1-use-safe-call-operator-"&gt;Fix 1: Use safe call operator &lt;code&gt;?.&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-kotlin" data-lang="kotlin"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Wrong
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;val&lt;/span&gt; name: String? = &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;null&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;println(name&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;!!&lt;/span&gt;.length) &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// NPE
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Correct
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;println(name&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;?.&lt;/span&gt;length) &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// null, no exception
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h3 id="fix-2-use-elvis-operator-"&gt;Fix 2: Use Elvis operator &lt;code&gt;?:&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-kotlin" data-lang="kotlin"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Wrong
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;val&lt;/span&gt; name: String? = &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;null&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;val&lt;/span&gt; length = name&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;!!&lt;/span&gt;.length &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// NPE
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Correct
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;val&lt;/span&gt; length = name&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;?.&lt;/span&gt;length &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;?:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;0&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// 0
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h3 id="fix-3-use-let-blocks"&gt;Fix 3: Use &lt;code&gt;let&lt;/code&gt; blocks&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-kotlin" data-lang="kotlin"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Wrong
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;val&lt;/span&gt; name: String? = getName()
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;println(name&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;!!&lt;/span&gt;.uppercase()) &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// NPE
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Correct
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;name&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;?.&lt;/span&gt;let {
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; println(&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;it&lt;/span&gt;.uppercase())
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;} &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;?:&lt;/span&gt; println(&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;Name is null&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;)
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h3 id="fix-4-check-lateinit-before-use"&gt;Fix 4: Check &lt;code&gt;lateinit&lt;/code&gt; before use&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-kotlin" data-lang="kotlin"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Wrong
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;class&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;User&lt;/span&gt; {
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;lateinit&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;var&lt;/span&gt; name: String
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;fun&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;greet&lt;/span&gt;() = println(&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;Hello, &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;$name&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;)
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;}
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Correct
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;class&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;User&lt;/span&gt; {
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;lateinit&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;var&lt;/span&gt; name: String
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;fun&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;greet&lt;/span&gt;() {
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;if&lt;/span&gt; (&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;::&lt;/span&gt;name.isInitialized) {
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; println(&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;Hello, &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;$name&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;)
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; } &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;else&lt;/span&gt; {
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; println(&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;Name not set&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;)
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; }
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; }
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;}
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 id="examples"&gt;Examples&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-kotlin" data-lang="kotlin"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Example 1: Safe null handling
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;fun&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;processUser&lt;/span&gt;(user: User?) {
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; user&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;?.&lt;/span&gt;let {
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; println(&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;it&lt;/span&gt;.name)
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;it&lt;/span&gt;.address&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;?.&lt;/span&gt;let { addr &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;-&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; println(addr.city)
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; }
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; } &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;?:&lt;/span&gt; println(&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;User is null&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;)
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;}
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Example 2: Default values
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;val&lt;/span&gt; config = mapOf(&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;host&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt; to &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;localhost&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;)
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;val&lt;/span&gt; port = config[&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;port&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;]&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;?.&lt;/span&gt;toIntOrNull() &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;?:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;8080&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 id="related-errors"&gt;Related Errors&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/kotlin/class-cast/"&gt;ClassCastException&lt;/a&gt; — wrong type cast at runtime&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/kotlin/illegal-argument/"&gt;IllegalArgumentException&lt;/a&gt; — invalid argument passed&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/kotlin/index-out-of-bounds/"&gt;IndexOutOfBoundsException&lt;/a&gt; — index beyond collection size&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;</description></item><item><title>[Solution] Java NullPointerException — Null Reference Fix</title><link>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/java/nullpointerexception/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/java/nullpointerexception/</guid><description>&lt;h1 id="nullpointerexception--null-reference-fix"&gt;NullPointerException — Null Reference Fix&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;A &lt;code&gt;NullPointerException&lt;/code&gt; (NPE) is thrown when your code attempts to access a method or field on a reference that points to &lt;code&gt;null&lt;/code&gt;. It is the single most common exception in Java and almost always signals a bug — either a missing null check or an unexpected null return value.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id="description"&gt;Description&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The NPE fires at the exact point where you dereference a null reference. Common variants include:&lt;/p&gt;</description></item></channel></rss>